~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

INSTALLATION
  * Rename settings.yml.default to settings.yml.
  * Edit the settings.yml to your specifications. Ensure your database information is correct.
  * Edit the config.ru file (if using Passenger) to your specifications.
  * Run!


